nATfGnZdSejgPDet5kIpe9jL3IOSIO8d77wFzbSw3Aa1eYLgfITz1cAUgfFvaDkNo_0kTKLqeUh2JF_POhnyv4LG4q5Vs9hyLAL7hX5fUkKFzVJOR7oJnIeCl6FFIBMfzijrTdEB0/YDN0zxzwq3sDBVeTuyeseTs81cxgB0dm/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="毒品暴力和财政风险等待着特朗普的新哥伦比亚盟友"&gt;提供的一切帮助&lt;/a&gt;来应对一系列艰巨的挑战，包括摇摇欲坠的电力网络、灾难性的公共财政以及可卡因贩运团伙的一波恐怖袭击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;泰国宪法法院就 120 亿美元紧急借款法令做出了有利于&lt;/strong&gt;政府的裁决，为总理阿努丁·占维拉古 (Anutin Charnvirakul) 带来了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Sf2ysUxkjjijFBzBK8qKB_cQ1RLwlhH7OkwhQtxWeZB1C16SAMxmOwzAPsPEtIpi5QdFJoHNneLtTNOS9iXzc3jGm3GHH4rMxgsYc3_oTxDpToM3icZIbW8BKL81C6YdJ-aN6wcYRr7DVfaJfgENCB0hON1SYblNLxBjhKoFTzV9wP2kcYQl0G4hFVMfC6Zn8BZdy2opAyrPN5LJGG-_oX90hajdlV3NjNHjOZPkryzTHILhEiwyF-1ItcDCIPqwXCvhv7k9Ab01fUTKwf0HwCORdpAXDCGV0CCC0DcQp1iim3x4w4zxC4IAXTazPMz4XQqngLtLzydGheS9Y4qgmjnfj3PW4r4BTRvrlqyBxXPDxmbGWraiqOIzdls8HEdIjndViXXXlEXzygOpeWoYqUaM0wi9Nn8Jkg4WY6JgsJ19k_rtmkLkXoNP66a9a0aRMQ0iBOa2ZTrzSEHNiJoOkpDpGIMqZeOK-YanY4D07fs2gchpQJzYd3ewaz7yCirXjBKjy9N6JeEap4mImeEBPQepzWwGBSX-eXLBR4XKcRTHXm7vo_44OMX9dcrx/Ydnpe7wQNCVIm9rspZRiZRY6m2w5i3Zg/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="泰国法院结清 120 亿美元危机贷款，阿努廷获胜"&gt;重大胜利&lt;/a&gt;。该判决消除了总理财政议程面临的最大法律障碍，使他能够推进旨在支持家庭和重振经济增长的刺激计划。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）做出&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/TURPm_MKodBHlhFcf_Nhnw1glN2u6Mlonb6X_herPqomUmrw9oez9cZYX3iPslp80LUUEplWAt3E6QbdEq3-N6JNGsd-uZELwl8RxHQJz6t_sTlSP3x2JkqIKi31UdXyafnx-3L8yKS9EhiysWegGya1adpaaceqp26e0Y2UnwXN6AcimGKUVes1yMAa6YHMmGTZlRK0_eQuN8E9nMA7fYldQUvKBibjGu15IZgWtbcV8MKOfLrjTntJc8RRHaM79ljhGIzjOUTrTJGE4EhE9pRFvOW7P9f9aKk3APIGWQhD3f-EXl5DgK0Qqtmu_fySk35M7EAMATL5p5UKY3701VzaDE1HocS99UQ3PQiYq7-uklimyAvJ2Mo2scq5sdvPhkqdQXoZB_M-Kvb44cKr5X7fUQHLi50UW6qykkSpkmpVA-P4GF4nrvz1ywbbaSRwa7TSX6j_4sLJ7P2lw6ye2HyVE