://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1148994&amp;amp;li=18896288&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=07082026210202&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550" style="display: block !important; width: 100% !important;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普称伊朗领导人是“恶毒的”、“邪恶的”、撒谎的“败类”。马克·钱皮恩在&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;《彭博社观点》中写道，&lt;/em&gt;或许确实如此，但这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/VarEb1bt_sS3RLF308PdI4DdPB4sC3e0nrfs_-oRQtDGPeGjEAVTvBo9P8Owd3PR_2GvewUqUcMK8dzHNzl6onSkqz7VfSKNEM-Uh9fsJZPV1uednkM5c0obo_qMVzxWn_1wXpCtKblTMFS3GGj0750yQgGPVM5-k4WO3zasEDs-nrTZgj5OXx4wMGNhHc6f4YntH66g-JMGRlrsp-7sJWUgFseO8R0ZwQjvFcTu5A9rftkrmQkJ8mPxmv7O7jz2j-4gaoH2M0BiO031g7M3m0AmpA_8M-N3ohQW5Yrhr_MKOt3q5aAazOn4RgB5vhGttni_rGRaMo15AGVblEU2I2nUhZPXAIQAzMIW9_s2KJGnhqFqWkrPiXDKVNG3QwjP25ScPFJ9LPM5H5-BXRGRaMlqfDv_opMoUQaxOcqtl96VwEKi2iWHBpF3qFBeDjFp1_xBHr3XPapmCmbT0NqPIHpDprAtdRDYNmpRG5hu7EC-Z6YIx_6NqJzK89edzkLHs3k/HNR7kunxnq7ank83HrIwIZoxKrR-1GGd/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普的伊朗停火注定会失败"&gt;并不是美国总统在霍尔木兹海峡陷入困境的根本原因&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;特朗普和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡选择发动一场战争，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PYkV9ogNb8qJ-W8e6WvDLKOsXc-0moBdSYoH2Nwr_CVhnFgvPFG1cPG4S6ofOAot6Ay--P16piLaDPfoJtvzDYnAIRtUsGJM3ZGX57LGz7m6JrO5L6T10guMIugHqXxaf-pjgyxPEacssP9DM9j8uFE2zsvjVBMXb9cV1escvbdVmH5KwnaHvwxuf06vmCLpBP0ldGs2Jg7pLjKAsN5aaE0evBbyKd7u1pBoGT-YInrUXsDwKs_-wn7gifMkCg0XrJpbsDJNsFXZ_1X6G1b3ayaWC3uNOgynvqvB1PCBv-60wNYhswnbGSdlX1E-KofyBP_b1h-_cDNebipmfhQl6yjP9rwpBe7CmurtxmYPXcQmFsAAEHcZAQ/8kujS_FFTSpz-KymaA1zw_zrC1z_tU_9/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="五角大楼保持沉默，美联社重现美国袭击导致 100 多名伊朗儿童死亡的事件"&gt;在此过程中造成数千人死亡&lt;/a&gt;，特朗普现在表示停火已经结束，进一步的外交将毫无意义。但钱皮恩写道，尽管伊朗试图扩大其对这条重要水道的影响力，但特朗普和美国海湾盟友的麻烦实际上源于他自己的谎言。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;不管特朗普怎么说，美国并没有赢得战争。伊朗也没有按照任何定义投降，更不用说“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/fLMXIBsPpjSHSArKG-pISE41sfr8ZDt8Iu6w3cVfBj71oDDmYh_DfOUxN0jqqEc0yfw0K0E14kWKL1ZmOtNGFMzDYahakBP5VwzkaM7eQcpH6ZI-WisM9Ekw8EVYwjok-ytEv3HEf0i1jwOUon2r1wuFHjeO55FGIaOMxg3wm5TfCdvMbUePKtqqKyiklDF9QwZXrr45o9KBvIaCC_Iu3AA8IIwowuuIro3rr6bbAQYaj-ELlBKwS1Cd1GtVbWmWCJjZoa0FzWx5UV9fGcafSw7-r0_vDYgV3vbuf5dBuDrWe1TKPQ7Evv_9pAwI_NQItFdwQErfte8KSEKchpPVFqRY73M65C_Lm3YTY6nad8HfsX74UBgz0P6ZFRPCweu50F85AVB3550SUe7naEG5EQwmq3Ac3hpQvAHn6Ze9Fn6kHm_cCiVf56yZ-fHMCbid8_4WEYTmTnJFyGNXSpZyzxE64qOtXHkJuSMbCu1F94vr94hbauza4aS2f5GMYAOzVKq84xsUdlRoBDrXaKq43TU/bBuAiz67QoSzfXp8-HRziSbUaQunP9nL/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普希望“无条件投降”，不会寻求与伊朗达成协议"&gt;无条件&lt;/a&gt;”投降了。事实上， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/M8LCzv_kGNP2JhmHsylO6VIXDFztiGffYCG75CY1fOUHqJF3Xw38GJvBkKD8nvwv8hiDy6468UXQQljh0PXK2LsOS9DEyRITVn8NCGoVwaS110STjg58LykgTkOgdMp6UFfHbzgsdSTPyGYppY7wL7ZUqowzMnk-6nM3cXRPkh5SZ0VhwoTX7uNlJuGj1lmMcAr57VS6ZuIk03rJpDLg894fJfZBichopaG20Fb02rf-KkTAl8ZeMyoMwfAJB7eg8dQV4XOWrOap-8cv1eFNUi-2pE2a5CjAKiabIbnxSDbvMt2K4UXgHbhvOVXmDviIDeEdOYa-4nfzlvoLiiJiOfJkZqN4RXGd3EYq2_JYRiRdEGEu5Iv7uT-rIJq2evJLnIlhrGvNTb_8OkljWlV5NKCY1doDWUxHHUdk6e4B2_j23J_BE-XtTWsr6lMScSdcat4WYyYI6YJBMktGJo4PH8qW8NACfQmrPirvu3OoA8BNMNfVvRBstlJXn7FuV0MDjPszhTk/_H0_5TIhl8KqMcjr95-gwPPD3KOVLrjK/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普表示伊朗停战结束，未来将有更多袭击，油价突破 80 美元"&gt;急于削减天然气价格&lt;/a&gt;的白宫同意的停火可以说是注定要失败的，其模糊的条款造成了一种本质上不稳定的局势。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;钱皮恩写道，其含糊性意味着双方会开始互相指责对方违反其条款，这只是时间问题。但直到周三， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/qADP7w9VgwublMwCIO2oHL4MEyKL4CkoTFYjX19fyar-BV5NRXe5svm7x_TqCT2ZCmRKanx4nJmKqK6_ibrBcquBFdxa